<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA49">
<l>koṇṭaṟṟāṉ mālvaraitāṉ mākaṭaṟṟāṉ kūriruḷtāṉ</l>
<l>vaṇṭaṟāp pūvaitāṉ maṟṟuttāṉ kaṇṭanāṭ</l>
<l>kāruruvaṅ kāṇṭōṟu neñcōṭuṅ kaṇṇaṉār</l>
<l>pēruruveṉ ṟemmaip pirintu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A cloud, a vast mountain, the dark sea, ample darkness,</l>
<l>a flower not left alone by bees, another thing – when we see them,</l>
<l>whenever it sees the colour of monsoon clouds [our] heart runs,</l>
<l>separating from us in the thought “it is Kaṇṇaṉ’s great form”.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
